&lt;li&gt;Manage learner enrollments, assignments, access requests, and course lifecycle updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain catalog accuracy, metadata, version control, and system hygiene across assigned LMS activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute standardized LMS reports, including participation, completion, and compliance tracking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform LMS quality checks prior to handoff or publishing to ensure setup accuracy and consistency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support uploads and related LMS administrative activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and escalate system issues, process gaps, or risks to the Associate or Senior Manager.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the first point of contact for Learning Inbox inquiries and LMS support requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot common LMS access, navigation, enrollment, completion, and learner account issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide timely and professional communication regarding support requests, status updates, and next steps.&lt;/li

